net.jodah.recurrent

Class Execution

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.jodah.recurrent.ExecutionStats
      • net.jodah.recurrent.Execution
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AsyncExecution

    public class Execution
extends ExecutionStats
    Tracks executions and determines when an execution can be performed for a RetryPolicy.
